  "title": "BIM Modeller",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Create and update BIM models based on contract drawings and latest information</li>\n  <li>Ensure on the integrity / quality of the models</li>\n  <li>Generate documentation and shop drawings for BIM models</li>\n  <li>Produce BIM model deliverables for construction, documentation and fabrication</li>\n  <li>Develop BIM models with the correct parameters and attributes for BIM based qualification and 4D simulation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Architecture / Civil Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years experience in civil &amp; structural, architectural BIM models related projects</li>\n  <li>Well versed in REVIT</li>\n  <li>Able to complete models, shop drawings in timely and quality manner</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in Revizto, Synchro 4D, Bently Open Building Designer will have an added advantage</li>\n</ul>",
